Lua-SDL2 (SDL 2.0 binding for Lua)
==================================

Lua-SDL2 is a pure C binding of SDL 2.0 for Lua 5.1, Lua 5.2 and LuaJIT.

Features
========

* Pure C binding, tries to be as portable as SDL 2.0,
* Very close to SDL library,
* Object oriented whenever possible (surfaces, textures, windows, etc.),
* Well documented.

Website
=======

The official website is hosted at:

	https://redmine.malikania.fr/projects/luasdl2

Documentation
=============

The documentation is available on the Lua-SDL2 wiki:

	https://redmine.malikania.fr/projects/luasdl2/wiki

Author
======

The Lua-SDL2 library was written by David Demelier <markand@malikania.fr>
